Package: sciCSR
Type: Package
Title: Single-cell Inference of Class Switch Recombination
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: c( person( given = "Joseph", family = "Ng",
                      email = "joseph.chifung.ng@gmail.com", role = c( "aut", "cre" ) ) )
Author: Joseph Ng [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Joseph Ng <joseph.chifung.ng@gmail.com>
Description: Package for inferring the dynamics of B cell state transitions using B-cell native processes (class-switch recombination, somatic hypermutation) from single-cell RNA sequencing data.
